{"id":498143,"date":[{"year":1969,"month":9,"day":6}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"275","ytitle":"","mtitle":"站在船台望北京","ftitle":"","authors":["钱国梁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱国梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天喜报满天霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地红旗遍地画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在船台望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不尽满腔的心里话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年船台写春秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年战斗在阳光下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱有千言万语怎表达。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一年，修破船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铆鎯头挥得两臂麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二年，造小船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铆钉枪冲天哒哒哒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年后，造大船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥舞焊钳笑哈哈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年呵，排排巨轮奔下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五湖四海腾浪花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船台风雨二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战马飞驰，步步闪光华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爬行主义”踩得稀巴烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋发图强向着高峰跨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船台风雨二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想抚育咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造船工人，堂堂英雄汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶天如金刚，立地似铁塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船台风雨二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握焊钳，眼望亚非拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱用红灿灿焊花绣大道——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上铁路通天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1969\\09\\6996020301.JPG\">"}]}